<blockquote>
  <p>Daniel NÃ¼st and Pebesma, Edzer. 2020. <strong>Practical reproducibility in geography and geosciences</strong>. Annals of the American Association of Geographers. doi:<a href="https://doi.org/10.1080/24694452.2020.1806028">10.1080/24694452.2020.1806028</a></p>
