<h2 id="the-rockerverse-packages-and-applications-for-containerisation-with-r">The Rockerverse: Packages and Applications for Containerisation with R</h2>

<blockquote>
  <p>Daniel NÃ¼st, Dirk Eddelbuettel, Dom Bennett, Robrecht Cannoodt, Dav Clark, Gergely DarÃ³czi, Mark Edmondson, Colin Fay, Ellis Hughes, Lars Kjeldgaard, Sean Lopp, Ben Marwick, Heather Nolis, Jacqueline Nolis, Hong Ooi, Karthik Ram, Noam Ross, Lori Shepherd, PÃ©ter SÃ³lymos, Tyson Lee Swetnam, Nitesh Turaga, Charlotte Van Petegem, Jason Williams, Craig Willis and Nan Xiao. <strong>The Rockerverse: Packages and Applications for Containerisation with R</strong>. The R Journal (2020), 12:1, pages 437-461. doi:<a href="https://doi.org/10.32614/RJ-2020-007">10.32614/RJ-2020-007</a></p>
